st steps away from the most significant monuments of ancient imperial Byzantium, such as the splendid Hagia Sophia, Hippodrome and Basilica Cistern and Ottoman masterpieces like Topkapi Palace and Blue Mosque.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>This property has only 6 rooms. All rooms are decorated in pastel colours. The rooms are small to medium size and all have a king size bed and wooden floor. All rooms have air conditioning, laptop size safe box, mini bar, double glazed windows, cable tv and a desk to work. All facilities are in perfect condition. The bathrooms are again extremely clean and in perfect condition.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>The hotel has been built in a traditional Ottoman edifice, its wooden facade reflects the nobility and charm of the ancient Istanbul. The Tria Elegance shares the same entrance as the Tria.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>The Tria Elegrance hotel has its own modern restaurant as well as a terrace with spectacular views of the bosphorus. They offer an interesting local and international selection of dishes.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>Short</Type><Text>The lobby is small and has some seating area's.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Rating><System>Stars</System><Score>40</Score><Description>Four star</Description></Rating><Rank>1</Rank></HotelElement>